PROBLEM STATEMENT:
Play through an AI ethics interactive fiction where confident AI outputs can be wrong, subtly wrong, or almost-right. 
Verify claims, code, and citations to learn practical habits for safe AI-assisted work.

HINTS:
The game pauses frequently. Press Enter at each continue prompt.
The flag is printed near the end of the story.

APPROACH:
After connecting to the game platform
There is a whole conversation happening between the normal user and his AI assistant
After every output given by the AI assistant, it asks the user to verify it or use them as given
User needs to verify every output and at the end of the conversation the flag is given.
